00:09.380 --> 00:11.382
Oh, hey, Dad.
How was work?

00:11.382 --> 00:12.783
I hate my job.

00:12.783 --> 00:15.246
The Captain's always
giving me a hard time.

00:15.246 --> 00:18.249
And today, he stuck me
with a rookie I have to train.

00:18.249 --> 00:19.790
Really? Who?

00:19.790 --> 00:21.552
Officer Katz.

00:24.755 --> 00:27.027
Is that a police cat?

00:27.027 --> 00:29.200
Yeah.
We used to have dogs,

00:29.200 --> 00:32.162
until the mayor appointed
an unmarried woman in her 40s

00:32.162 --> 00:33.434
Chief of Police.

00:34.705 --> 00:36.767
The point is I've had it.

00:40.211 --> 00:43.344
You know, if your job
makes you so unhappy,

00:43.344 --> 00:45.516
maybe you should think about
doing something else.

00:45.516 --> 00:47.648
Really?
 Why not?

00:47.648 --> 00:50.221
I mean you always told me
to pursue my dream

00:50.221 --> 00:52.123
and do something
that makes me happy.

00:52.123 --> 00:54.185
I did say that,
didn't I?
 Mmm-hmm.

00:54.185 --> 00:55.556
You're absolutely right.

00:55.556 --> 00:56.557
(LAUGHS)

00:57.728 --> 00:58.729
(LAUGHS)

00:59.630 --> 01:02.633
Captain, this is Darryl.

01:02.633 --> 01:04.495
I've decided
to pursue my dreams.

01:04.495 --> 01:05.495
Dad, what are you doing?

01:06.737 --> 01:08.739
I'm tired of your
stupid rules,

01:08.739 --> 01:10.571
and your boring paperwork,

01:10.571 --> 01:12.443
and your constant nagging.

01:12.443 --> 01:15.476
"Where's your badge?
Where's your patrol car?

01:15.476 --> 01:17.708
"What happened
to that suspect?"

01:17.708 --> 01:19.750
Dad, stop!

01:19.750 --> 01:23.354
Oh, yeah? Huh.
Well, you can't fire me
because I quit.

01:23.354 --> 01:25.156
And you know what
you can do with your job?

01:25.156 --> 01:27.658
You can put it where
the sun don't shine.

01:27.658 --> 01:29.420
Like in a cabinet
or Seattle.

01:31.822 --> 01:33.594
Uh...
 (SIGHS)

01:33.594 --> 01:36.367
I feel so much better.
Thank you, Chyna.

01:38.129 --> 01:40.701
I can't believe
you just quit your job.

01:40.701 --> 01:43.404
Why? You told me
to follow my dream.

01:43.404 --> 01:44.605
So, what's my dream?

01:44.605 --> 01:45.706
I don't know!

01:46.607 --> 01:48.539
Wow!

01:48.539 --> 01:50.711
Well, you really
should have thought
this through better.

